    {
      "english": "Commercial pain points",
      "kanji": "",
      "pain_points": [
        "Fulfil Order
        "C1.1.1 Using Sales Order, XX (Delivery Head) schedules delivery [vehicle, capacity, route]
         C1.1.2 Warehouse generates ~Picklist and picks LPG/products.
         C1.1.3 Warehouse generates Delivery Receipt (2 DRs and 2 CRs).
         C1.1.4.1 Warehouse submits DR to Acctg to make General Ledger and Inventory.
                C1.1.4.2 Driver gets Delivery Receipt (DR) from Warehouse XXX? for multiple clients. Driver and Pahinante drive to client locations.",
                C1.1.4.3 No Delivery/For Pick up. Warehouse XX gives DR to customer for signature.
         C1.1.5.1 Pahinante weighs and delivers the cylinders. He retrieves the empties cylinder/s and weighs it in the vehicle."
        "      C1.1.5.2 Client signs DR and picks up the items and returns empty cylinder. Client leaves. 
         C1.1.6 P gives XX memo to client, containing credit gain (kg) and acknowledges receipt (via sign)." 
        "C1.1.7 Driver returns to Plant. Driver and Warehouse Staff weigh empty cylinders in Plant. Driver writes the weights." 
        "C1.1.8 Driver submits record and signed DR and AR to Acctg."
        "C1.1.9 Acctg Staff reconciles open General Ledger with signed DR and AR. Acctg Staff reconciles inventor in Gsheet."
      ]
    },
